timing_context...sdc_exceptions(25.10)  timing_context...sdc_exceptions(25.10)

Name
       timing_context_apply_port_sdc_exceptions

Syntax
       timing_context_apply_port_sdc_exceptions {true | false}

       Default: false

       When  set  to true, the software will consider path exceptions on block
       constraints in the hierarchical context flow.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

